12. Definitions
App means the mobile application available in the Apple App Store and the Google Play Store.
Site means the website which we provide at http://www.splid.app and associated domains.
Group means a group which you can create with our App.
Personal Data means information that can be associated with an identified or directly or indirectly identifiable natural person.
Technical Usage Data means information we collect from your phone, computer or other device that you use to access the Sites or Services. Technical Usage Data tells us how you use our App, for example whether and when the App crashed and how frequently you use certain features.